Resource Profile: Encounter: Inpatient Encounter

Official URL: http://va.gov/fhir/StructureDefinition/EncounterInpatientEncounter Version: 1.4.15
Draft as of 2025-04-30 Computable Name: EncounterInpatientEncounter

This StructureDefinition contains the maps for VistA file PTF (45) to us-core-encounter.

​See also the FHIR Shorthand.

Use Case Overview

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: Debt Portal ChargeItem[charges]
  • CapabilityStatements using this Resource Profile: Lung Cancer Screening and Lighthouse Patient Health API
